## Notes for Creating Custom Credit Card Component
https://www.lloydsbank.com/credit-cards/help-and-guidance/credit-card-numbers-explained.html

## Credit Card Numbers per Provider
- Mastercard numbers start with a 2 or 5.
- Visa card numbers start with a 4.
- American Express numbers start with a 3.

## Credit Card Flip Tutorial
https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_css_flip_card.asp
- Want to use this to create card flip effect for front / back of credit card
- This will not be a hover effect, but will trigger off of input focus
- May add a button to allow manual card flips

